{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1784039709219", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "太好了——我现在已经掌握了关键的事实依据。让我来总结一下发现：\n\n**关键先前工作发现：**\n1. Wu 等人，\"Cross-lingual Transfer for Speech Processing using Acoustic Language Similarity\" (arXiv 2111.01326, ASRU 2021) — 早在 2021 年就提出了使用声学语言相似度进行跨语言 ASR 迁移。这是一个直接的先行研究。\n2. Kim 等人，\"Improving Cross-Lingual Phonetic Representation of Low-Resource Languages Through Language Similarity Analysis\" (arXiv 2501.06810, 2025) — 通过语言相似度分析进行跨语言语音表示。\n3. Mitsumori 等人，\"Cross-lingual Data Selection Using Clip-level Acoustic Similarity\" (Interspeech 2025) — 低资源 ASR 中基于片段级声学相似度的数据选择。\n4. Ambikairajah 等人，\"A Study of Speech Embedding Similarities Between Australian Aboriginal and High-Resource Languages\" (Interspeech 2025) — 这是论文中引用的前身工作（参考文献 [ambikairajah2025study]），仅进行了句子级的 LID 相似度分析，没有进行下游 ASR 评估。\n5. arXiv 2607.04814 — \"Evaluating the Effect of Linguistic Relatedness on Cross-Lingual Transfer in Large Multilingual ASR\" — 将语言相关性应用于非洲语言的跨语言 ASR 迁移。\n6. \"Predicting positive transfer for improved low-resource speech recognition using acoustic pseudo-tokens\" (2024) — 使用声学特征预测正向迁移。\n\n现在让我来撰写完整的评审意见。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "0ada5674-66cf-42af-8319-9fe17730d7f7", "uuid": "4b2b76bc-61bf-4213-a7c6-9cef003e1ba9"}
